# API测试文件
# 使用VS Code的REST Client扩展或其他HTTP客户端测试

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 用户注册
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试用户",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 用户登录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 获取用户信息
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 创建书签
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Google",
  "url": "https://www.google.com",
  "folder": "搜索引擎",
  "tags": ["搜索", "工具"],
  "description": "谷歌搜索引擎"
}

### 获取书签列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookmarks
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 搜索书签
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookmarks/search?q=google
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 创建密码
POST http://localhost:3000/api/passwords
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "site_name": "GitHub",
  "site_url": "https://github.com",
  "username": "myusername",
  "password": "mypassword123",
  "notes": "开发账号",
  "category": "开发工具"
}

### 获取密码列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/passwords
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 获取特定密码
GET http://localhost:3000/api/passwords/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE